<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Store</title>
  <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <![endif]-->
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="114x114" href="touch-icon-iphone4.png" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
    <div class="navbar-inner">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="btn btn-navbar" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".nav-collapse">
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        </a>
        <a class="brand" href="#">Black Swan Central</a>
        <div class="nav-collapse">
          <ul class="nav">
            <% %w(Monday Tuesday Wednesday Thursday Friday Saturday Sunday).each do |day| %>
              <li><%= link_to day, "/?day=#{day.downcase}" %></li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span9"><%= yield %></div>
      <div class="span3">
        <h2>About Yoga</h2>
        Yoga is a physical, mental, and spiritual discipline, originating in ancient India. The goal of yoga, or of the person practicing yoga, is the attainment of a state of perfect spiritual insight and tranquility while meditating on the Hindu concept of divinity or Brahman.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
